    <div data-cid="4917629">
        <div class="main review-item" id="4917629">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/truely-moment/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/truely-moment/" class="name">candy yang</a>

            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2011-04-22" class="main-meta">2011-04-22 14:24:50</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4917629/">贫穷也是一种气质</a></h2>

                <div id="review_4917629_short" class="review-short" data-rid="4917629">
                    <div class="short-content">

                            真的是非常搞笑的一部漫画，同时也让人感觉很温馨。太郎的形象真的是太经典了，那种对钱的执着和痴迷已经到了无以复加的境界，让人大爱。我也很佩服他的父母，真的是太天兵了，难怪会养成山太郎那样的个性。不过他们都很团结，没有彼此埋怨和苛责，真的是很温馨的一家人。

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4917629-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_4917629_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_4917629_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="4917629" title="有用">
